!!!
html(lang="en")
  head
    title QA Checklist - 2nd Developer
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge,chrome=1")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width")
    link(href="css/styles.css", rel="stylesheet", type="text/css")
   body
    h1 QA Checklist - 2nd Developer
    hr

    h2 Best practices
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Fix broken links - http://www.brokenlinkcheck.com/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Spelling and grammar
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Browser Check (PC & Mac) Chrome, Firefox, Safari, IE7-10 - Browsershot or Virtual Machines
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check website in iPhone &amp; Android Phone
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check website in iPad
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Remove 'www' subdomain - .htacces / IIS
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site have a meaningful and helpful 404 error page that works from any depth in the site?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use friendly URLs?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site have a favicon?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the project up to date on its documentation on the wiki?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are all passwords logged in LastPass?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is master branch the production branch?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the project in Git properly?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is there an up-to-date executable SQL file?

    h2 Analytics
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Uptime monitoring
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Traffic analysis (Google Analytics, other tracking tools + special click tracking)

    h2 Performance
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Google Page Speed score of 90+ - https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Yahoo YSlow score of 85+ - http://developer.yahoo.com/yslow/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are JS/HTML/CSS and images optimized?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check correct database indexing

    h2 Usability
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label HTML5 compatibility check
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is there a clear visual hierarchy?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are heading levels easy to distinguish?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the site’s navigation easy to understand?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the site’s navigation consistent?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use consistent and appropriate language?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site have a sitemap page and contact page? Are they easy to find?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is there a link to the home page on every page in the site?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are links underlined?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are visited links clearly defined?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are all forms validated with JavaScript and back-end technology?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are all form validation errors easily understood and informative?

    h2 SEO
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label SenSEO score of 85+ - https://addons.mozilla.org/en-us/firefox/addon/senseo/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label robots.txt
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label XML sitemap & submitted to Google and other search engines
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Page Titles are important; ensure they make sense and have relevant keywords in them.   
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Create metadata descriptions for important pages.   
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check for canonical domain issues (e.g. variations in links to http://site.com http://www.site.com http://www.site.com/index.html should be reduced to a single consistent style)   
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Ensure content is marked-up semantically/correctly (h1, etc.) 
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check for target keyword usage in general content   
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check format (user/search engine friendliness) of URLs
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Configure Google Webmaster Console and Yahoo! Site Explorer 

    h2 Code quality
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label HTML validation - http://validator.w3.org/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label CSS validation - http://jigsaw.w3.org/css-validator/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Run CSS Lint - http://csslint.net/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Run JSLint/JSHint - http://www.jslint.com/ & http://www.jshint.com/
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use a correct Doctype?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use a Character set?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use any CSS hacks?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use unnecessary classes or ids?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the code well structured?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site have JavaScript errors?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Degree of separation between content and presentation
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use CSS for all presentation aspects (fonts, colour, padding, borders etc)?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are all decorative images in the CSS, or do they appear in the (X)HTML?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are sprites being used?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the code well documented?

    h2 World ready
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check all functionality 
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check search functionality (including relevance of results)
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Test all forms (e.g. contact us, blog comments), including anti-spam features, response emails/text, etc. 
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check all external links are valid   
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are 301 redirects in place?

    h2 Accessibility
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Accessibility validation
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label WAI-ARIA LandmarksAre “alt” attributes used for all descriptive images?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Do any aspects of the layout break if font size is increased? (remember, users can control and override the CSS)
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site use accessible forms?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is there delayed responsiveness for dropdown menus (for users with reduced motor skills)?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the content accessible with CSS switched off or not supported?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is the content accessible with images switched off or not supported?
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Does the site work well when printed?

    h2 Security
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Follow best practices (e.g. salting and hashing passwords)
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Cross-site scripting
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Cross-site request forgery
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Protect any sensitive pages (e.g. administration area)
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Set-up email/SMS monitoring/alerts (e.g. for errors, server warnings); consider internal and external monitoring services 
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Transaction logging if necessary
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Is spam prevention in place (e.g. honeypot)
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Are all software (e.g. WordPress, CakePHP) and libraries (e.g. jQuery) up to date?

    h2 Content, Consistency &amp; Style
    ul 
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Ensure no test content on site
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check all ‘Hidden Copy’ (e.g. alt text, transcriptions, text in JavaScript functions)

    h2 Misc
    ul
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Check all requirements and that all requirements are met
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Add humans.txt
      li
        input(type="checkbox")
        label Provide team with logins for all levels (Admin, user, etc) and any testing credientials (e.g. fake credit cards)